# Reeple Currency Converter

## Introduction
This is a React Native application that allows users to convert between multiple currencies using live exchange rates. The app features a clean, user-friendly interface and includes robust error handling.

## Features
- Select both source and target currencies from a list of 10 supported currencies.
- Fetch and display real-time exchange rates using a third-party API.
- Convert amounts in real-time as you type.
- Handle API errors gracefully with user-friendly messages.

## Supported Currencies
- USD (United States Dollar)
- EUR (Euro)
- GBP (British Pound)
- CAD (Canadian Dollar)
- NGN (Nigerian Naira)
- JPY (Japanese Yen)
- AUD (Australian Dollar)
- CNY (Chinese Yuan)
- INR (Indian Rupee)
- ZAR (South African Rand)

## Setup Instructions

### Prerequisites
- Node.js and npm installed
- React Native CLI installed
- Android Studio for Android development

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/acmekrish/reeple-currency.git
   cd reeple-currency
